metadata.content:
# K-344 - Behind the scenes[]

K-344 appeared in "Tatooine Rhapsody," a short film in the Star Wars: Visions series directed by Taku Kimura, produced by Studio Colorido, and released on Disney+ on September 22, 2021. She was voiced by Masayo Fujita in Japanese and by Shelby Young in the English dub. K-344 was first pictured in the initial preview trailer for Visions on July 3, 2021, and was identified in the cast list posted on StarWars.com on August 17.
